cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD

Reasoning: 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely category as the paper deals with anti-patterns detection and their impact on program comprehension and maintainability. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses the internal detection rules of various anti-patterns detection approaches. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is likely as the paper proposes a machine-learning based ensemble method for anti-patterns detection. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper extensively uses machine-learning algorithms. 
- cs.SD (Software Development) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with improving the quality of software development by detecting and addressing anti-patterns.
